title: Witcher 3: GOG; Preorder Exclusive Bonus Content
description: Here, scurvy seadogs! Grab it while still sizzling hot! Normally, i would NEVER up something from that site, especially since i did not originally buy or own it myself, because said site is DRM-FREE and fights against the way other companies do business (business which is abusive to their clientele), but as of late, many contradictions started popping up there and even more cheap, bad imitations of aforementioned calamities, started getting between us and our game. So, a pirate is no stranger to unfair game. That is why we deliver with a pinch of salt. Enjoy
